comprehensive_precision.title: Precision-related Metrics
comprehensive_precision.description: Precision: ratio of true positives to combined true and false positives; formula: P = TP/(TP + FP). Recall: ratio of true positives to combined true positives and false negatives; formula: R = TP/(TP + FN). F1 Score: harmonic mean of the recall and precision; formula: F1 = 2 x P x R/(P + R).

comprehensive_precision.title: 精度相关指标
comprehensive_precision.description: 精确率，正确预测的正例数和预测正例总数的比值。P=TP/(TP+FP)。召回率，正确预测的正例数和实际正例总数的比值。R=TP/(TP+FN)。F1值，精确率与召回率的调和均值。F1=2*P*R/(P+R)。
